Package gui

The gui package contains all the elements that will be used to create and use the graphical user interface

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FileMenu
    The class FileMenu generate the menu File in the frame.
    Frame
    The class Frame generate all components in the graphic user interface.
    HelpItemMenu
    The class HelpItemMenu generates the content of the action of each item in the Help Menu
    HelpMenu
    The class HelpMenu generate each item in the help menu, depends of the plugins found.
    Menu
    The class Menu generates the bar that will contains each menu.
    ToolsMenu
    The class ToolsMenu generates each item in the Tools menu, depends of the plugins found.
